headline: BofA Trims TPG Valuation while Reaffirming Confidence in Growth Strategy
summary: TPG Inc. (NASDAQ:TPG) is included among the 13 Best Income Stocks with Highest Upside Potential. On February 24, BofA lowered its price recommendation on TPG Inc. (NASDAQ:TPG) to $72 from $77. The firm maintained a Buy rating on the shares. BofA said the change reflects updated EPS estimates across several brokers, asset managers, and exchanges […]
